title: [Lissanne's General Store]
[Lissanne's Armory]
description: Blue watered silk walls rise from a mistwood plank floor.  Just above a brass flowerpot hangs a pearl-handled filigreed mandolin, and a mistwood beam ceiling completes the picture.  A jewel-inlaid caddy and a glass-topped mistwood counter stand side by side in the middle of the room.
